===========================================================
Dockerfile for a SciON Capability Container image
===========================================================

Based on scioncc/scion_python


DOCKER IMAGE
============

sudo docker build -t scioncc/scion_cc:3.0.0 .


USAGE
=====

sudo docker run --rm -it scioncc/scion_cc:3.0.0 /sbin/my_init -- bash -l
